    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/e3e825034d30fa890ebf45332548fe04.avif?t=1733936454\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>神秘的女研究员苗沫为什么出现在古墓中？她在和久寻相遇前经历了什么样的可怕遭遇？战斗和逃生，是你此刻唯一需要考虑的事情！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/76da2ec40a282021b7a2744d02537d38.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/76da2ec40a282021b7a2744d02537d38.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/76da2ec40a282021b7a2744d02537d38.mp4?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>西南边陲，古老村寨的祭坛下，传来了阵阵毛骨悚然的声响。神秘的女研究员苗沫，只身一人穿行于祭坛下这座庞大的汉代古墓中，墓中道路错综复杂、怪物横行……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/1d43c4d9fee0cd14a0b8ec70a4736234.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/1d43c4d9fee0cd14a0b8ec70a4736234.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/1d43c4d9fee0cd14a0b8ec70a4736234.mp4?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>今天是寨子中举行特殊仪式的日子，为什么她会突然出现在古墓中，出现在下一任蛊婆——久寻的面前？<br>在这个面如止水的女研究员身后，似乎隐藏着太多的疑问，但现在的她，已经没有一秒钟可以耽搁，她要不惜一切代价，完成她的秘密任务！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/3d6a469113f619d984466757e0f2bb19.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/3d6a469113f619d984466757e0f2bb19.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735720/extras/3d6a469113f619d984466757e0f2bb19.mp4?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>她能达到自己的目的么？",
